vta.core

LoadUop

Related Doc: package core

class LoadUop extends Module

LoadUop.

Load micro-ops (uops) from memory, i.e. DRAM, and store them in the uop-scratchpad. Currently, micro-ops are 32-bit wide and loaded in group of 2 given the fact that the DRAM payload is 8-bytes. This module should be modified later on to support different DRAM sizes efficiently.
